        factors play critical roles in the recognition of <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">promoters</ENAMEX>
        by <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">RNA polymerase</ENAMEX>. In several systems, individual sigma
        factors are known to regulate the differential expression
