        generated in a promoter-trap plasmid containing two
        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">reporter genes</ENAMEX>. The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">library</ENAMEX> is transformed into strain
        expressing the transcription factor, and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">recipients</ENAMEX> with
